# Project Rules for Raypx

## Language Requirements
- All code comments MUST be written in English
- All commit messages MUST be written in English
- All documentation MUST be written in English

## Code Style
- When writing or modifying code, ensure all comments are in English
- When suggesting commit messages, always use English
- When explaining code or making suggestions, use English

## Commit Message Format
- Commit messages should follow conventional commit format
- All commit messages must be in English
- Example: `feat(auth): add user authentication`
- Example: `fix(email): resolve template rendering issue`

## Code Comments
- Function/class comments should be in English
- Inline comments should be in English
- TODO/FIXME comments should be in English

